{"title":"tieu de moi","slug":"tieu-de-moi","content":"<h2 id=\"load-h2-0\" data-index=\"0\">1, Tổng quan về selector trong Jquery.</h2>\n<p>tieu de moi</p>\n<p>-Nếu như bạn l&agrave; một người đ&atilde; t&igrave;m hiểu về&nbsp;<a href=\"https://toidicode.com/hoc-css-can-ban\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CSS</a>&nbsp;rồi, th&igrave; bạn học selectors trong Jquery sẽ rất nhanh . Bởi v&igrave; selectors trong Jquery cũng hỗ trợ c&uacute; ph&aacute;p giống như CSS.</p>\n<p>VD: Chọn thẻ c&oacute; id l&agrave; banner.</p>\n<p>Trong CSS:</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">css</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-css hljs \"><span class=\"hljs-id\">#banner</span><span class=\"hljs-rules\">{\n    <span class=\"hljs-rule\">//<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">code\n}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Trong Jquery:</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-javascript hljs \">$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'#banner'</span>);</code></pre>\n<p>-Nhưng nếu bạn chưa t&igrave;m hiểu về CSS th&igrave; qua b&agrave;i n&agrave;y bạn sẽ cũng hiểu được về&nbsp;<strong>Selectors trong &nbsp;jquery</strong>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"load-h2-1\" data-index=\"1\">2, C&aacute;c Selector trong Jquery.</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"load-h3-0\">Chọn tất cả c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh phần của HTML.</h3>\n<p>-Để chọn tất cả c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh phần trong HTML th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng ta sử dụng c&uacute; ph&aacute;p:</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-javascript hljs \">$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'*'</span>);</code></pre>\n<p>-Lưu &yacute;:&nbsp;Nếu một trang web c&oacute; qu&aacute; nhiều thẻ HTML th&igrave; khi d&ugrave;ng thẻ n&agrave;y sẽ hao tổn rất nhiều t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n (client).</p>\n<p><strong>VD</strong>: CSS cho tất cả c&aacute;c thẻ trong trang web.</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-javascript hljs \">$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'*'</span>).css(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'color'</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">'red'</span>);</code></pre>\n<p><a class=\"btn-demo\" href=\"https://toidicode.com/live/?id=189\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Xem Kết Quả</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"load-h3-1\">Chọn theo element HTML</h3>\n<p>-Để chọn theo&nbsp;element&nbsp;trong trang web th&igrave; ch&uacute;ng ta sử dụng c&uacute; ph&aacute;p:</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-javascript hljs \">$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'elementName'</span>);</code></pre>\n<p><strong>VD</strong>: CSS cho tất cả c&aacute;c thẻ div trong trang.</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-javascript hljs \">$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'div'</span>).css(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'color'</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">'red'</span>);</code></pre>\n<p><a class=\"btn-demo\" href=\"https://toidicode.com/live/?id=190\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Xem Kết Quả</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"load-h3-2\">Chọn theo class</h3>\n<p>-Để chọn theo t&ecirc;n class của thẻ HTML th&igrave; c&aacute;c bạn sử dụng c&uacute; ph&aacute;p:</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"code-badge-pre\"><code class=\"language-javascript hljs \">$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">'.className'</span>);</code></pre>\n<p><strong>VD</strong>: CSS cho tất cả c&aacute;c thẻ t&ecirc;n class l&agrave; '<em>website</em>'</p>\n<div class=\"code-badge\">\n<div class=\"code-badge-language\">javascript</div>\n<div title=\"Copy to clipboard\"><em class=\"fa fa-copy code-badge-copy-icon\">copy</em></div>\n</div>","createAt":1649297161115,"id":"5202798b-3023-440b-9a7d-b189b41a96c8"}